# Sharadha Stores Batch Inventory Tracker - SMTP Configuration Template
# Copy this file to '.env' in the same folder and fill in your credentials.

# Your Gmail address used as the sender (e.g. sender@gmail.com)
SMTP_EMAIL=your_email@gmail.com

# Your Google Account App Password (NOT your normal Gmail password).
# How to get a Google App Password:
# 1. Go to your Google Account (https://myaccount.google.com).
# 2. Select 'Security' on the left navigation.
# 3. Under 'How you sign in to Google', make sure '2-Step Verification' is turned ON.
# 4. Search for 'App passwords' in the search bar or navigate to it.
# 5. Enter a name for the app (e.g. 'Sharadha Stores Batch Tracker') and click 'Create'.
# 6. Copy the generated 16-character passcode and paste it below without spaces.
SMTP_PASSWORD=abcd efgh ijkl mnop
